Via Bremen   [DESSAU [18.10? 86? 5-6N?]--two overlapping circular cancels in black, one in blue] [Deutsche Reichs Post 10 Pfenning 10--two red stamps with a crowned German eagle]
Mrs. Hermann Raster
fr      391. West Jackson street

        Chicago, Ill.
        America

Because Annie had no time to write yesterday or today I am sending you the letter she wrote Saturday without help or dictation or (Newmann Raefee's note)
Probably almost 1880 or so -
